ies/salariestax/exemption/employee.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Ftaxes%2Fsalaries%2Fsalariestax%2Fexemption%2Femployee.htm&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU4pVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=041a815b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/salaries/salariestax/exemption/employee.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港是按地域來源徵稅，凡因任何職位或受僱工作或退休金而獲得的入息，如果是於香港產生或得自香港，不論有關入息是否已在其他稅收管轄區繳稅，均須課繳薪俸稅。在決定受僱工作的來源地時，以下3項都是考慮的因素：<br />\n僱傭合約洽談、訂立和執行的地方；<br />\n僱主的居住地；以及<br />\n支付僱員薪酬的地方。"},{"pid":"b8ffcaf2c396571fe4b34dec243a51570fc2e394","tid":2327605,"uid":55493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"時差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />半夜同香港同事開會"},{"pid":"96c30e8d0ea2ef9c75f5d43520d9d03e7837a245","tid":2327605,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12fe63c0539b87b6f0d32ee57209d669b97f27be","tid":2327605,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:33:42.000Z","msg":"同事：全部外國人有世界各地，唔洗返office，除非壞電腦<br />\n出糧：香港branch出糧，用香港銀行：HSBC<br />\n交稅：已預期要交英港兩邊稅，不過稅後都可維持生活<br />\n<br />\n有乜野可能出現既問題，請巴打提出，先謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2bfea683c14111d3d30e3488fc160637eae524","tid":2327605,"uid":114175,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8ffcaf2c396571fe4b34dec243a51570fc2e394","tid":2327605,"uid":55493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"時差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />半夜同香港同事開會"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743b3dca7a9a5de3d737f0eb501e843384042160","tid":2327605,"uid"